OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778613067
OL,3,CTwo Irish passengers from virus-hit
OL,4,Cship land in Dublin
OL,6,FAn Irish Government jet landed in the
OL,7,FRepublic of Ireland on Sunday night
OL,8,Fafter being sent to Tenerife to
OL,9,Fevacuate two passengers who were on a
OL,10,Fvirus-hit cruise ship.
OL,12,FThe MV Hondius, which is at the centre
OL,13,Fof the hantavirus outbreak, docked in
OL,14,FTenerife in the Canary Islands on
OL,15,FSunday morning.
OL,17,FSpanish authorities have been
OL,18,Fconducting health checks and
OL,19,Fdisembarking passengers.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
