FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778613067
OL,3,CTwo Irish passengers from virus-hit
OL,4,Cship land in Dublin
OL,6,FThe Irish aircraft flew to and from
OL,7,Fthe island from Baldonnel Aerodrome on
OL,8,FSunday.
OL,10,FFlight-tracking websites showed the
OL,11,Fplane left Tenerife for Ireland at
OL,12,Faround 5.40pm and landed back at the
OL,13,Fmilitary air base in west County
OL,14,FDublin shortly after 9pm.
OL,16,FTwo ambulences were seen leaving the
OL,17,Fairport just before 9.30pm.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778613067
OL,3,CTwo Irish passengers from virus-hit
OL,4,Cship land in Dublin
OL,6,FThe Department of Health said two
OL,7,Fpassengers would be accompanied by
OL,8,FHealth Service Executive (HSE) medics
OL,9,Fduring the "aeromedical evacuation".
OL,11,FThey were said to have followed
OL,12,Fisolation protocols on the ship and
OL,13,Fwere in "good health".
OL,15,FThey were due to be taken to an HSE
OL,16,Ffacility where they would be monitored
OL,17,Fwhile quarantining, a process which
OL,18,Ffollows international guidance.
OL,26,@qD@LOUqD@cO]uD@IOUuD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778613067
OL,3,CTwo Irish passengers from virus-hit
OL,4,Cship land in Dublin
OL,6,FOn Saturday, a Department of Health
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "If they become
OL,8,Fsymptomatic, they will be assessed and
OL,9,Ftreated as appropriate."
OL,11,FIn a statement, the department said:
OL,12,F"The return of passengers and crew
OL,13,Ffrom MV Hondius has been carefully
OL,14,Fplanned and guided by public health
OL,15,Fauthorities to ensure safety for
OL,16,Feveryone ` these measures protect
OL,17,Fcommunities while respecting the
OL,18,Fdignity and well-being of those
OL,19,Freturning home."
OL,26,@oD@TOUqD@XO]tD@AOU{D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
