OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778613067
OL,3,CTwo Irish passengers from virus-hit
OL,4,Cship land in Dublin
OL,6,FSpanish authorities said on Sunday
OL,7,Fthat no passengers on the ship were
OL,8,Fshowing symptoms of the virus and the
OL,9,Fdisembarkation process was "proceeding
OL,10,Fwell".
OL,12,FThey began the evacuation of the ship
OL,13,Fby nationality and ferried passengers
OL,14,Fto port by small boat.
OL,16,FPassengers were told to leave their
OL,17,Fluggage on the ship and were only
OL,18,Fallowed to take a small bag with
OL,19,Fessential items.
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778613067
OL,3,CTwo Irish passengers from virus-hit
OL,4,Cship land in Dublin
OL,6,FThe first group to be evacuated was
OL,7,Fmade up of 14 Spanish nationals who
OL,8,Fwere flown to a hospital in Madrid.
OL,10,FWhile they were being bussed from the
OL,11,Fport at Granadilla de Abona to
OL,12,FTenerife South Airport, some
OL,13,Fpassengers, wearing blue PPE, waved
OL,14,Fand gave thumbs up gestures as they
OL,15,Fpassed watching media.
OL,17,FThe World Health Organisation (WHO)
OL,18,Fsaid its goal was to finish the ship's
OL,19,Fevacuation, with the exception of 30
OL,20,Fcrew members remaining on board, by
OL,21,F7pm on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778613067
OL,3,CTwo Irish passengers from virus-hit
OL,4,Cship land in Dublin
OL,6,FThose crew members and a nurse from
OL,7,Fthe Netherlands, as well as the body
OL,8,Fof a passenger who died on board, will
OL,9,Fremain on the ship, which will sail to
OL,10,FRotterdam in the Netherlands where it
OL,11,Fwill undergo disinfection, the WHO
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FWHO director-general Dr Tedros Adhanom
OL,15,FGhebreyesus told a press conference in
OL,16,FTenerife that the outbreak was "not
OL,17,Fanother Covid and the risk to the
OL,18,Fpublic is low".
OL,26,@xD@`OUzD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
