OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778613067
OL,3,CTwo Irish passengers from virus-hit
OL,4,Cship land in Dublin
OL,6,FThe organisation has said that as this
OL,7,Fis the first documented outbreak of
OL,8,Fhantavirus on board a ship, a highly
OL,9,Fprecautionary approach was being taken
OL,10,Fout of "an abundance of caution".
OL,12,FThey said on Saturday there had been
OL,13,Fsix confirmed hantavirus cases linked
OL,14,Fto MV Hondius and four patients were
OL,15,Fin hospital.
OL,17,FIt said that eight cases, including
OL,18,Fthree deaths, had been reported ` with
OL,19,Fone previous suspected case being
OL,20,Freclassified after testing negative
OL,21,Ffor hantavirus.T
OL,26,@rD@HOUrD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/8
